{"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"LINK","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"href":"/posts/last-fm/"}}},"blocks":[{"key":"lfs01","text":"In a separate post, you can look through the data in a slightly different way, with links to the entries for each item. But here, you can break down the history by year, quarter, month, and even week. Click on an item to see the monthly breakdown.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"offset":3,"length":13,"key":0}],"data":{}},{"key":"lfs02","text":"This app is pretty experimental, and I'm not sure how long it will last. But it's a fun project to work on, and I'm glad I did it. There will be errors. Enjoy!","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"lfs03","text":"Artists","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"lfs04","text":"Albums","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"lfs05","text":"Yearly Plays","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]}
